{
  "stem": "9538.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We also had no idea what it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And big chimneys-- three big chimneys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And out of these chimneys came the-- these ashes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We thought, it's a factory of some sort.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They herded us into a shower room-- the women.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, don't ask me how many.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Quite a few of us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They herded us into the shower room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had to undress first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had to leave everything we had-- you know, this gray dress they gave us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And only our shoes we could take with us into the shower room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They gave us a piece of soap, and there we waited in the shower room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And no water came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then they herded us out again the other side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They gave us striped prison garbs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did not come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It never came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The water never came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They opened the gates on the other side of the-- of the shower room, yes, and let us go out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later on, we saw that there not only was this one shower room, they had three or four of them next to one another, and they were gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were in this gas chamber waiting for the water to come, thinking a shower room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "See, at that time, we had never heard of-- of-- of gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was-- we were lucky they let us go out the other side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then there were prisoners standing there who had positions-- some that I told you already.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a green triangle, and they were the criminals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the pink were the Jehovah's Witnesses, and the lilac were the homosexuals.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had usually-- they were in charge of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the SS women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They gave us these clothes, and we were herded into barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
